                            <br>
                            <a href="https://ngrl-dbmu.atlassian.net/browse/NDI-221" class="csg-mark-link" style="border: none; background: transparent; color: #0052cc; text-decoration: none;">NDI-221</a> All Edit Pages: Hide ID Field If Editing New Unsaved Record
                            <br>
                            <a href="https://ngrl-dbmu.atlassian.net/browse/NDI-220" class="csg-mark-link" style="border: none; background: transparent; color: #0052cc; text-decoration: none;">NDI-220</a> Crop For CWR List Views Need DataTable Logic
