                            <br>
                            <a href="https://ngrl-dbmu.atlassian.net/browse/NDI-169" class="csg-mark-link" style="border: none; background: transparent; color: #0052cc; text-decoration: none;">NDI-169</a> Change "Recent" Setting to "Past Month" In All Lists
                        </p><h3 class="csg-h3" style="font-style: inherit; color: #172B4D; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 32px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -0.008em;">Task</h3><p class="csg-p" style="margin: 0; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 7px; padding-top: 7px; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; line-height: 24px; font-size: 14px;">
                            <a href="https://ngrl-dbmu.atlassian.net/browse/NDI-197" class="csg-mark-link" style="border: none; background: transparent; color: #0052cc; text-decoration: none;">NDI-197</a> Enlarge Font of ID Numbers on Edit Pages
                            <br>
                            <a href="https://ngrl-dbmu.atlassian.net/browse/NDI-180" class="csg-mark-link" style="border: none; background: transparent; color: #0052cc; text-decoration: none;">NDI-180</a> On CWR Map Edit Page, Only Show "Common Name' Field if "Is Crop" is "Yes"
                            <br>
                            <a href="https://ngrl-dbmu.atlassian.net/browse/NDI-178" class="csg-mark-link" style="border: none; background: transparent; color: #0052cc; text-decoration: none;">NDI-178</a> All Lists Must Use Standard DataTable Functions (Sort, Paging)
                            <br>
                            <a href="https://ngrl-dbmu.atlassian.net/browse/NDI-175" class="csg-mark-link" style="border: none; background: transparent; color: #0052cc; text-decoration: none;">NDI-175</a> Citation Lookup Must Filter by Species and its Synonyms
                        </p>
                    </div>


                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger pull-right" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- /.modal-content -->
        </div>
        <!-- /.modal-dialog -->
    </div>


